HEADWORD: Somniferous
<hw>Som*nif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>somnifer</ets>; <ets>somnus</ets> sleep + <ets>ferre</ets> to
bring.]</ety> <def>Causing or inducing sleep; soporific; dormitive;
<as>as, a <ex>somniferous</ex> potion</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Walton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

